      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a pristine E92 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering featuring the S65 4.0L V8 and its iconic 8,400 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission and M Variable Differential Lock for an unfiltered analog experience. The mechanical integrity is superlative; rod bearings and throttle actuators have been preventatively serviced with comprehensive documentation. The factory carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof is flawless, and the suspension geometry remains tight and responsive. Inside, the Novillo leather sport seats show no bolster compression or wear. Entirely stock, this vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring the individual throttle bodies and VANOS system operate with factory precision. A true turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
